headline: Urban Outfitters Stock Scores 95-Plus Composite Rating
summary: Urban Outfitters stock saw its IBD SmartSelect Composite Rating rise to 96 Friday, up from 90 the day before.  Urban Outfitters stock is currently forming a flat base, with a 60.90 buy point.  See if the retail stock can break out in heavy trade at least 40% above average.
